title: All Play and No Work
description: Mega Man must resist the influence of a prankster bot named Chaotique, whose devil may care ideology appeals to the overworked superhero, until his friends pay the price for his dalliances.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Past Car
description: Tulip takes a risk trusting an old foe.

title: Falafel's in Jail
description: Apple & Onion must get Falafel out of jail for a crime he did not commit.

title: Camp Unikitty
description: The gang's set for an awesome weekend of glamorous, easy-living camping out in fun, friendly nature! But when Hawkodile challenges their idea of camping (it should be a fight for survival in the hostile woods), the gang switch places, with Hawkodile living a luxurious glamp life while Unikitty and the others survive in the wild. Will Unikitty still believe the "great outdoors" are all that great if they meet their doom by natural causes?

title: El vagon de la piscina de pelotas
description: El grupo es confrontado por una nueva y extraña fuerza en una aventura por un vagón lleno de pelotas.

title: Rainy Day
description: The girls get into trouble when left to entertain themselves on a rainy day.

title: Steven Universe Panel - NYCC 2019
description: Creator Rebecca Sugar and voice talent DeeDee Magno Hall (Pearl), Estelle (Garnet), Michaela Dietz (Amethyst) and Sarah Stiles (Spinel) perform songs from Steven Universe the movie and discuss it in this live panel from New York Comic Con.

title: Joyride
description: At a rummage sale with Uncle Andrew, Axel and Zoe must stop Madcap from turning her long-lost tank toy, Joyride, into an agent of mayhem!

title: License to Drill
description: Mega Man teams up with Bert Wily to take down Drill Man, whose plan to construct hundreds of drill shaped high rises has put Silicon City in both aesthetic and physical danger!

title: El vagon del pasado
description: Tulip se arriesga al confiar en un viejo enemigo.

title: Helping Cattus Help
description: The search for a mythical creature gets rather metaphysical when the equally elusive Cattus' assists the mission.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: Fashion Bears
description: In order to abide by the clothing policy of their favorite Boba shop, the Bears get some new outfits. But with new looks come new lives including office work, fashion modeling and even falling in love!

title: The 11th Alien Part 2
description: After discovering that Vilgax has joined forces with the Weatherheads to trick him into turning over the Omnitrix, Ben must not only overcome his doubts, but fully embrace his new powers if he is to beat his foes.

title: Steven Universe Future - Catch Up Trailer
description: Catch up on everything going on with Steven and the gems in Steven Universe Future so far!  This trailer covers the most important events of the first ten episodes of Steven Universe Future.

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: Aspirations
description: The Gangreen Gang is actually committing brilliant crimes. But behind every great gang, there has to be a great woman.

title: Motel
description: Following an insect mishap Clarence's house needs to be fumigated forcing Mary, Chad, and Clarence into a motel. In the meantime, Clarence and Chad learn a bit about responsibility while Mary contemplates a life of letting go.

title: Legends of Mr. Gar
description: Rad and Enid reminisce about when they started working at the bodega and learned how amazing Mr. Gar really is.

title: We're Captured
description: Boxman captures KO, Enid and Rad, but seems a little distracted.

title: Elect to Decline
description: Noville wants to impress Vambre with a new Magisword from the Cave of Stuff, but the Cave Weirdos are in election mode and horrible smear campaigning is making Noville's simple task impossible!

title: Charlie Ball
description: After Panda gets injured on the basketball court, the Bears invite Charlie to be on their basketball team. But when Charlie gets too good, he starts to ruin all the fun of the game.

title: True Kinda Love Official Music Video
description: : The official music video for "True Kinda Love" by Estelle feat. Zach Callison from Steven Universe The Movie.

title: Expreso De Gran Estres
description: Durante una transmisión en vivo del nuevo tren bala transcontinental, La Grange se cuela para ganarle al tren. Pero Ben se suma a la diversión, iy no se detendrá ante nada para salir victorioso!

title: Creek Cart Racers
description: A high-speed race with a high-stakes prize may be too much for Craig and his friends.

title: Pantalones Movedizos del Tiempo
description: Oscar y Erizo se enteran de la existencia de unas arenas movedizas que les permiten viajar en el tiempo.

title: Head Chef
description: Mao Mao faces off with Badgerclops in a competition to determine whether cooking (and being a hero) is an art or a science.

title: Mystery Sleepover
description: KO, Enid and Rad attempt to solve a mystery.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Worm Bin
description: After his mom gets a worm bin, Jeff deals with the gross reality that he has a tub of bugs living in his kitchen, and Clarence obsesses over feeding the worms.

title: Career Day
description: Robin forces the other Titans to forget their dreams and find regular, boring jobs.

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: The Visitor
description: A vision leads Finn to a friendly civilization and a mysterious crash site.

title: The 11th Alien Part 1
description: With new Omni-Enhancements in tow, Ben looks to save a town from a sudden mudslide, but his heroics are short lived once Vilgax appears to warn our hero about the consequences of the Omnitrix's mysterious new alien.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: The Wild Hunt
description: A fierce creature is terrorizing the Candy Kingdom but before Finn can slay the beast, he must first overcome a guilty conscience.

title: Crossover Nexus
description: When KO finds himself trapped inside an mysterious place, he encounters other Cartoon Network Heroes and they band together to escape.

title: Fuerte Williams
description: iCuando Craig no puede ir al Arroyo, él y su madre deciden construir el fuerte de cobijas más grande del mundo!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: El cuarto oscuro
description: Tras ser rechazado por un club de fotografía, Val intenta conseguir una foto del legendario Chupacabra para demostrar su valor.

title: The Hands of Time
description: Master Wu mistakenly tries to single-handedly complete a battle he began decades ago against Acronix, one of the twin Hands of Time. But the arrival of the first Time Blade, a weapon with the power to speed up time, sends the Ninja to the Monastery just in time to rescue their master from certain doom.

title: Visita Monstruosa
description: Los monstruos se ponen nerviosos cuando su Dios monstruo llega de visita.

title: Exercising the Demons
description: When a severe screen addiction turns the kids into lazy deadbeats, Chef brings in a professional to whip them into shape.

title: The Hero
description: Gumball and Darwin are determined to prove to their dad that he is their hero, at any cost!

title: Changeable Terraingable
description: Personality conflicts between Vambre and Prohyas come to a head as the Warriors miraculously manage to ace a mission at an ever changing labyrinth.

title: #FightAtTheMuseum
description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

title: Steven's Birthday
description: Steven has a birthday party out at the barn, and decides he has some growing up to do.

title: El Onceavo Alienigena Parte 1
description: Con sus nuevas Omni-Mejoras, Ben intenta salvar una ciudad de un repentino alud. Pero su heroísmo dura poco, porque llega Vilgax a advertirlo de las consecuencias del misterioso alien del Omnitrix.

title: Demonios internos
description: Los Fantásticos encuentran la forma de salir de Vestroia, pero descubren que en realidad están en un mundo paralelo.

title: Disappearing Act
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a young wannabe magician by teaching her a new trick.

title: Buscando Misiones
description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

title: West in Pieces
description: It's the old west and Mojo the Kid has robbed the first bank ever and forced the sheriff out of town and it is up to the Steamypuff Girls to save the day at a high-noon showdown.

title: The Big Sleep
description: When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes.

title: Independent Together Song
description: Independent Together (feat. Ted Leo, Deedee Magno Hall & Aimee Mann) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: Spider Sense
description: When a monster ruins their relaxing vacation, the Girls run into a familiar face.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Quien se llevo a Pan
description: Cuando Pan desaparece de la fiesta de Unikitty, ila princesa lidera una búsqueda para encontrarlo y desenmascarar al secuestrador de tostadas!

title: Punos Fuertes
description: Harto de perder cuando juega a los videojuegos contra su padre, Craig busca entrenarse en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Queen of Bees
description: Ben, Gwen and Grandpa Max arrive in Bismarck, North Dakota for its annual celebration of bee pollination, bringing them face-to-face with Queen Bee and a bold new scheme, forcing Ben to conquer his new fear of bees!

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Kill' Em with Kindness
description: Pops wants to be friends with someone.

title: Una epoca de traidores
description: Lloyd lucha con su papel como maestro en entrenamiento y Nya hace todo lo posible para reiniciar a Zane.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Classic Titans
description: To prove his point about classic superhero cartoons, Control Freak sends the Titans to a former version of Teen Titans Go!

title: Problemas Dentales
description: A Puppycorn se le cae su primer diente, y Unikitty está emocionada por su hermanito, ique ahora recibirá la visita de la legendaria Hada de los Dientes! Pero cuando el Hada de los Dientes no aparece, Unikitty y sus amigos asumen la responsabilidad. ¿Acaso se meterán demasiado rápido y con demasiada soltura con los dientes sueltos y tocarán un nervio sensible?

title: Bear Cleanse
description: A doctor tells the Bears to go on a cleanse to improve their health. But when Grizz realizes he can only eat what grizzly bears eat, he starts to lose his mind.

title: Genie President
description: Robin hatches a plan to get rich off pennies, but Starfire believes they are magical.

title: The Tower
description: Finn doesn't like any of the new arms the princesses give him, so he builds a tower into space to find his dad and get his old arm back.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Legend of Boggy Ben
description: Lion-O has gotten a hold of the last jar of Thundersnaps, the best cookies Thundera had to offer! But a difficult to open cookie jar is gonna send Lion-O and Cheetara chasing down a legend, a Boggy Ben-related legend.

title: Una linea en la arena
description: Jay lucha por defender la casa de su familia.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Stratificados
description: Los Fantásticos emprenden una misión en el misterioso mundo laberíntico de Vestroia para buscar a Strata El Cazador y liberar a los Bakugan que tiene presos.

title: Don't Be An Icarus
description: Robin tries to tell some Greek myths but the other Titans give their own fractured versions instead.

title: Atrapados en la jungla
description: Aún perdidos en Vestroia, Los Fantásticos experimentan los efectos de la Célula Núcleo que altera sus cuerpos, y se encuentran cara a cara con el monstruo Bakugan, Tiko.

title: El Coleccionista
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic pierde una de las preciadas monedas de Val, Val hace un trato con un misterioso coleccionista de antigüedades para reemplazarla, pero el trato tiene consecuencias terribles.

title: Happily Ever After Live Performance
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar and voice talent DeeDee Magno Hall (Pearl), Estelle (Garnet) and Michaela Dietz (Amethyst) perform the song "Happily Ever After" from Steven Universe the Movie, live at New York Comic Con.

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Gut Model
description: Muscle Man becomes a model.

title: Garden of Evil
description: Poison Ivy takes control of Swamp Thing using his vegetative powers to overwhelm Gotham with dangerous plants.

title: All Good in the Wood
description: When Suna and Ashley's science project turns into a hungry blob monster, Mega Man must team up with Wood Man to shut down the experiment gone wrong before it devours the city!

title: Prank Call
description: Lion-O wants to prove to the ThunderKittens that he's not just some boring old adult, like Tygra, even if it means ignoring his instincts and messing with an obviously evil crystal.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Message Received
description: Steven has doubts about believing in everyone.

title: Dawn Before Dusk
description: Dawn Before Dusk, Part 1: The AO meet Benton Dusk discovering that their quiet little corner of the world is about to become much, much larger./Dawn Before Dusk, Part 2: Benton Dusk reveals that the AO have been indentified as persons of interest by powerful corporations including Philomena Dusk's AAAnimus.

title: Lift With Your Back
description: Rigby wants to prove to Mordecai that he can earn a paycheck from another job.

title: Phantasm Chasm
description: After getting sucked into Jared's favorite board game, Buttercup is forced to team-up with him in order to save her sisters.

title: Awakenings
description: The dramatic conclusion of the Never-Realm saga, in which old friends are reunited and the power of friendship is pitted against the corrupting power of the Scroll of Forbidden Spinjitzu.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: #AunqueSeaGigante
description: Karen Beecher siempre es molestada en la escuela. Pero cuando el centro comercial es atacado por una monstruosa super villana llamada Giganta, Karen descubre que la diminuta Bumblebee puede ser la única suficientemente pequeña para salvar el día.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Words
description: Darwin is too polite to speak his mind, so Gumball teaches him to be direct via an epic battle of insults.

title: The Engine
description: Tulip makes it to the front of the train and is faced with a choice.

title: Of Predators and Prey Part 2
description: While trapped in Khyber's ship, Ben learns details about the origin of the Nemetrix, and the link between Khyber, Malware, and Dr. Psychobos! (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Tyrannopede.)

title: I See a Funny Cartoon in Your Future/Octi-Gone
description: I See a Funny Cartoon In Your Future: The girls have the rare task of fighting a medium who is committing petty thefts./Octi-gone: When Bubbles finds a single leg of Octi's, she sets out to find out who took her toy and what they want from her.

title: Other Friends Live Performance
description: Sarah Stiles (voice of Spinel) performs the song "Other Friends" from Steven Universe the Movie, live at New York Comic Con.

title: Problemas Lunares
description: La Luna se entristece cuando Oscar pierde su brazalete de la amistad.

title: Let Us Adore You Song
description: Let Us Adore You (feat. Christine Ebersole, Lisa Hannigan, Patti LuPone & Sarah Stiles) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: The Grades
description: Miss Simian discovers a failed test from Gumball's past that brings down his grade point average. This means he has to retake kindergarten all over again, much to her delight. But by demoting him Miss Simian has inadvertently brought herself down, and they're left with no choice but to team up if they want things back to normal.

title: The Best Team
description: When Madcap and his minions crash a soapbox derby, the team must stop the baddies and help Axel - stuck in a car with Luka - cross the finish line!

title: Grup Jam
description: Grup invents the "new" sport of basketball, but the stakes are too high for the Warriors to let him play the Galacton team, as the winner shall rule the Kingdom of Rhyboflaven.

title: Falls, Falls, Falls
description: Team Tennyson looks to take in the sights of the Shoshone Falls, but when they arrive to find Steam Smythe siphoning off the water, it is up to Ben to distract the steam punk baddie long enough to allow Grandpa Max and Gwen the time to shut down the hydropower plant and save the Falls.

title: The World
description: The amazing world of Elmore is full of inanimate objects that aren't nearly as inanimate as you might hope!

title: Roughing It Up/What's the Big Idea
description: Roughing It Up: The girls and the Professor set out on an old-fashioned vacation to the Townsville Swamp. Trouble is, Fuzzy and his nephews are there, too./What's the Big Idea: 20 story high Powerpuff Girls spell disaster for Townsville when they delicately try to stop Mojo from taking over.

title: The Boy Who Cried Lechuza
description: After faking an injury to get out of work, Vic gains sympathy from everyone while unknowingly attracting attention from a dangerous mythical creature.

title: Padres y amigos
description: Osamu Kazami viene para llevarse a su hijo Shun a casa y se encuentra con un obstáculo que no había contemplado.

title: That's Not My Baby/Simian Says
description: That's Not My Baby!: The girls save a baby from a monster attacking Townsville but can't find the mother. Can these three superheroes manage to take care of one little baby?/Simian Says: When the Narrator is mysteriously bound and gagged, Mojo Jojo takes over his job, ordering the girls to steal for him all around Townsville.

title: Steven Universe the Movie: Drift Away Song
description: Drift Away (feat. Sarah Stiles) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: Rook Tales
description: Rook's former teacher will preserve Revonnahgander traditions at any cost.

title: Presenting Joe Cuppa
description: KO tries to help his favorite comedian, Joe Cuppa.

title: Aventura en el laberinto
description: Perdidos en el laberinto de Vestroia, Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a poderosas fuerzas que parecen luchar por el control del planeta.

title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

title: Messy Bessy
description: Seth must clean his room and learn to be a neater person in order to keep Messy Bessy from making his life a nightmare.

title: Dia de los Trabajos
description: Robin obliga a los demás Titanes a olvidar sus sueños y a conseguir trabajos normales y aburridos.

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Apple and Onion have to defend the music store from instrument theft to get a key to the store.

title: Carroneros
description: Lloyd se da cuenta de que hacerse cargo del debilitado Maestro Wu no es una tarea fácil.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Nos Capturaron
description: Box-man captura a K.O., Enid y Rad, pero parece un poco distraído.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Dia de elecciones
description: En un esfuerzo por demostrarle a Master Frown que no es una tirana, Unikitty acuerda celebrar una elección para ver quién será la nueva princesa del Unireino. En una situación sorpresiva, Master Frown toma una ventaja temprana en las encuestas. Unikitty descubre que Frown gana porque está haciendo trampa. ¿Recurrirá Unikitty a sus propios trucos sucios para ganar las elecciones o permanecerá fiel a sí misma y seguirá tratando de ganar gracias a su amabilidad?

title: Fort Williams
description: When Craig can't go to the Creek, he and his mom decide to build the biggest blanket fort in the world!

title: The Hatching
description: The Ninja learn more about the Krux and Acronix, the two fallen Elemental Masters known as the Hands of Time, and are sure this threat has finally been eliminated. But with Wu out of action and suffering from the effects of the Time Punch, the Ninja discover a new enemy in their midst, the Vermillion Warriors. And the Ninjas have no idea who controls them.

title: La incubacion
description: Los Ninja descubren un nuevo enemigo en medio de ellos.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: Titanes Clasicos
description: Para demostrar su punto de vista sobre los dibujos animados clásicos de superhéroes, iControl Freak envía a los Titanes a una versión antigua de Jóvenes Titanes en Acción!

title: Industrias Dusk Parte 1
description: Los Fantásticos conocen a Benton Dusk y descubren que su pequeño mundo está a punto de volverse mucho más grande.

title: Lost and Found
description: Mordecai and Rigby go get a wallet.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: High Stress Express
description: During a live feed of the new transcontinental bullet train, La Grange enters the picture to outrace the train, but Ben joins in on the fun and will stop at nothing to come out on top!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Roadtrip Ruckus
description: Richard has decided to take Unikitty and the gang for a pleasant and relaxing 10 hour road trip. At first everyone is against the trip, but they soon start to have fun. Unfortunately, their idea of fun is not Richard's.  He soon begins to give in to his inner road-rage. To make matters worse they are being chased by a killer semi-truck, and their car has been invaded by weird bug hitchhiker.  Will Richard loose it, or will the trip be a great success?

title: Scavengers
description: In the midst of an epidemic of mysterious metal thefts by the Vermillion Warriors, Lloyd realizes stepping up and taking over for the ailing Master Wu is not an easy task.

title: Victor y la Lechuza
description: Después de fingir una lesión para no tener que trabajar, Vic se gana la compasión de todos mientras que, sin saberlo, atrae la atención de una peligrosa criatura mítica.

title: Who Took Toast
description: When Toast disappears from Unikitty's party she leads a search to find him and expose the toast-napper.

title: The Vault
description: When Finn starts sleepwalking and dreaming about the Green Lady he filed away in his memory vault, Jake and BMO help him tap into his repressed memories to uncover a secret past. Who is the Green Lady? And how is she connected to Finn?

title: Es mi Fiesta
description: Oscar y Erizo planean una fiesta de cumpleaños sorpresa para Susie.

title: Questing For Quests
description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

title: It Could've Been Great
description: The Gems take a trip to the moon.

title: An Egg-stremely Bad Idea
description: Hoping to 'brighten her day', Izzy and Owen pimp out Gwen's egg chair. But when it ends up in a museum run by angry chickens, they must retrieve it before Gwen destroys the daycare in a temper tantrum of unspeakable darkness.

title: Leyendas del Senor Gar
description: Rad y Enid recuerdan la época en la que comenzaron a trabajar en el almacén y entendieron lo fabuloso que es el Sr. Gar.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Birthday
description: Jeff and Sumo expect no one to show at Clarence's birthday party, just like last year. When dozens of kids arrive, the boys struggle to get face time with Clarence, the popular party host.

title: Viaje en Carretera
description: Richard decidió llevar a Unikitty y a la banda a un agradable y relajante viaje de 10 horas por la carretera. Al principio todo el mundo está en contra del viaje, pero pronto empiezan a divertirse. Por desgracia, su idea de diversión no es la de Richard. Pronto, el conductor comienza a sucumbir ante su furia interior al volante. Para colmo de males, los persigue un semirremolque asesino, y su coche ha sido invadido por un extraño autoestopista. ¿Richard perderá la razón o el viaje será un gran éxito?

title: Industrias Dusk Parte 2
description: Benton Dusk revela que Los Fantásticos son considerados personas de interés por poderosas corporaciones como AAAnimus.

title: Rad Monster Party
description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System—the home of the monstrous aliens!

title: Lame Lockdown
description: The head scientist puts Mordecai and Rigby on a 24-hour lockdown inside the Dome, but they want to sneak out and see one of their favorite bands.

title: Presentando a Joe Kaffi
description: K.O. intenta ayudar a Joe Kaffi, su comediante favorito.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Galaxy Jest
description: Joker is abducted into space by Mongul to entertain Mongul's troops. Unless the Justice League can re-capture him in time, a Joker gas bomb will go off in Gotham threatening the city.

title: Isn't It Love? Live Performance
description: Estelle (voice of Garnet) performs the song "Isn't It Love?" from Steven Universe the Movie, with assistance from show creator Rebecca Sugar and DeeDee Magno Hall (voice of Pearl) live at New York Comic Con.

title: Dulce Acido
description: Craig se embarca en un alucinante viaje mientras trata de comer la golosina más ácida del Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Thin Yellow Line
description: Finn and Jake infiltrate the Banana Guard ranks and stumble upon a conspiracy.

title: Keeping Up with the Kryptonians
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk shows Supergirl and Superman that their innate goodness might not be so pure when he takes them to a parallel world where their counterparts are impossibly aggressive and spoiled.

title: Jefe por un dia
description: Cuando Chata deja que Vic sea el jefe del puesto de tacos por un día, él decide despedir a Val, lo que trae consecuencias desastrosas.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: Steven Universe the Movie: Happily Ever After Song
description: Happily Ever After (feat. Zach Callison, Deedee Magno Hall, Estelle, Michaela Dietz, Tom Scharpling, Uzo Aduba, Jennifer Paz & Shelby Rabara) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: Carrera en el Arroyo
description: Una carrera de alta velocidad con un premio de alto riesgo puede ser demasiado para Craig y sus amigos.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Inside Job
description: In a "Fantastic Voyage" like adventure, Atom shrinks Batman and Wonder Woman so they can enter Superman's bloodstream and destroy a lethal nanite virus.

title: True Kinda Love Live Performance
description: Creator Rebecca Sugar and voice talent Estelle (Garnet) perform the song "True Kinda Love" from Steven Universe the Movie, live at New York Comic Con.

title: El Onceavo Alienigena Parte 2
description: Ben descubre que Vilgax se ha unido a los Weatherheads para obligarlo a entregar el Omnitrix. Ahora no solo deberá superar sus dudas, sino también aceptar sus nuevos poderes, si es que quiere derrotar a sus enemigos.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: Fishing Trip
description: Mel learns that Chad has never taken Clarence fishing, a tradition he sees as a rite of passage, and decides to remedy this with a bonding trip for all the boys! Split into two groups, Mel and Clarence learn a bit about each other while Chad struggles with the ins and outs of fishing.

title: Power Punchers
description: Fed up with losing in video games to his Dad, Craig seeks training in the Creek.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: In the Garden of Good and Eddie
description: When the girls try a quick-fix on their neglected veggie garden, they are left with a giant, mooching tomato worm they must care for.

title: Fire Man in the Hole
description: While hiking on a dormant volcano, Aki sets out to retrieve Ashley's lost camera and, as Mega Man, to stop Fire Man from setting off an eruption!

title: Sour Candy Trials
description: Craig goes on a mind-bending journey as he tries to eat the most sour candy in the Creek!

title: The Dark Room
description: After getting rejected by a photography club, Val tries to get a picture of the legendary Chupacabra in order to prove himself.

title: The Collector
description: When Vic accidentally loses one of Val's prized coins Val makes a deal with a mysterious antiques collector to replace it, but the deal has terrible consequences.

title: Home on the Run/Top Slot
description: Home on the Run: We are introduced to Shun's mysterious backstory, his relationship with his industrialist father and desire for a closer knit family./Top Slot: Dan and Shun butt heads on how best to make the AO a real team amidst growing threats including the mysterious Shargo Ronin.

title: Secret Book Club
description: Kelsey starts a super secret book club to introduce Craig and JP to the joys of reading.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: La locomotora
description: Tulip logra llegar al frente del tren y debe afrontar una decisión.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Outbreak
description: When Dr. Psychobos steals a part out of the Omnitrix, causing chaotic side effects, it's up to Ben, Rook, and a small team of Plumbers get everything back to normal. (Introducing new Ben alien Kickin' Hawk, temp Ben alien Walkatrout, Upchuck Rook.)

title: Ghostfreaked Out
description: Ben's internal demons get externalized when Ghostfreak escapes from his watch and becomes a full fledged being on his own. The renegade alien then realizes he needs to meld with Ben's DNA in order to survive.

title: Drift Away Live Performance
description: Creator Rebecca Sugar and voice talent Sarah Stiles (Spinel) perform the song "Drift Away" from Steven Universe the Movie, live at New York Comic Con.

title: El vagon inacabado
description: El grupo entra a un vagón sin terminar e intenta arreglarlo.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Capture the Flag
description: Water balloon fights, warring factions and the risk of jail time, everything is on the line when Clarence and friends play the biggest game of capture the flag yet! Everyone wants to take home the crown, and the power to control the neighborhood's juice boxes.

title: A Change of Face
description: In Salem Massachusetts, Ben, Gwen and Max once again go up against Charmcaster, whose goal is to switch souls with Ben and possess the Omnitrix. However, Charmcaster first accidentally switches identities with Gwen, and then as spells fly back and forth, Ben and Gwen even end up in one another's bodies before they team up to get rid of Charmcaster once and for all.

title: Pijamada Misteriosa
description: KO, Enid y Rad intentan resolver un misterio.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Campamento Unikitty
description: La pandilla está lista para un fin de semana increíble, para vivir la buena vida acampando con estilo en la divertida y amigable naturaleza. Pero cuando Halcondrilo desafía su idea de acampar (debería ser una lucha por la supervivencia en los bosques hostiles), la pandilla intercambia el lugar con él: ahora, Halcondrilo vive una vida de campamento glamoroso mientras Unikitty y los otros sobreviven en la naturaleza. ¿Seguirá creyendo Unikitty que la "increíble naturaleza" es tan increíble si encuentran su destrucción por causas naturales?

title: Steven Universe the Movie: Other Friends Song
description: Other Friends (feat. Sarah Stiles) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: You Can't Handle the Tooth
description: Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus must rescue Pizza Steve from the Tooth Fairy.

title: Trading Day
description: When they think each others' lives are easier, the heroes switch roles.

title: El Popular Banana Split
description: Erizo y Max descubren una escuela diminuta cuando, por accidente, un experimento científico los encoge.

title: Nexo Creativo
description: Cuando KO queda atrapado dentro de un lugar misterioso, se encuentra con otros héroes de Cartoon Network y todos se unen para escapar.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: A Time of Traitors
description: Kai's investigation of a Vermillion Warrior Helmet leads him to discover Krux is alive and well in NinjaGo, living under an assumed identity. Meanwhile, as the Vermillion Warriors go on a kidnapping spree, Lloyd struggles with his role as master-in-training and Nya does her best to reboot Zane, who was knocked off line in his first battle with the Vermillion.

title: Pesadilla de verano
description: Drago y los otros Bakugan de Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a una nueva y poderosa amenaza, solo para dejarlos preguntándose si todo habrá sido un sueño.

title: Club de Lectura Secreto
description: Kelsey crea un club de lectura supersecreto para introducir a Craig y JP en las alegrías de la lectura.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Las manecillas del tiempo
description: El maestro Wu intenta completar una batalla que comenzó hace décadas contra Acronix.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Pizza Steve's Past
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang learn of Pizza Steve's past stint in the food service industry. Pizza Steve wasn't always the Pizza Steve they know and love.

title: What's the Big Idea?
description: Pizza Steve and Mr. Gus try to help Uncle Grandpa get an idea.

title: The Unfinished Car
description: The gang enters an unfinished train car and tries to fix it.

title: Demon Prom
description: Trigon makes Raven attend her prom and she brings along the other Titans to upset him.

title: Rooms
description: The Bears switch bedrooms for the night and get a glimpse of the living space of one of their brothers. But the deeper they go, hidden secrets are revealed.

title: Tooth Trouble
description: Puppycorn loses his first tooth and Unikitty's excited for her little bro, now he​ ​gets a visit from​ ​the​ ​legendary Tooth Fairy!​ ​But when the Tooth Fairy is a no-show, Unikitty and her friends take on the mantle and responsibilities. But will they play too fast and loose with loose teeth and hit a raw nerve?

title: Election Day
description: In an effort to prove to Master Frown that she is no tyrant, Unikitty agrees to hold an election to see who will be the new princess of the Unikingdom. In a shock, Master Frown takes an early lead in the poles. Unikitty discovers Frown is winning because he's cheating. Will she resort to her own dirty tricks to win the election or stay true to her self and try to win by being nice?

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Cuddle Monster
description: After being told by Chata that they can't get a pet, Vic & Val adopt a wild lizard, unaware of its magical properties, and decide to keep it secret from Chata.

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: El vagon cromado
description: El grupo se encuentra con una cara familiar en un vagón espejado.

title: #BatallaEnElMuseo
description: Supergirl siempre confía en su fuerza, pero necesitará mas que músculos para impedir que la astuta Catwoman robe unas valiosas gemas del museo de ciencias.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Behind the Curtain: Steven Universe the Movie
description: This documentary follows Rebecca Sugar and the Crewniverse as they lead the audience on the journey of creating Steven Universe the Movie. From Cartoon Network Studios to Zuma Beach, the fans get an in-depth look at the formation of the story, the process of writing the music, and the collaboration between musicians, the Crewniverse, and the cast, while experiencing the locations where they took place.

title: Un verdadero lider
description: Entre diversas amenazas, como el misterioso Shargo Ronin, Dan y Shun no pueden acordar la mejor forma de convertir a Los Fantásticos en un verdadero equipo.

title: #SheMightBeGiant
description: Karen Beecher is always getting picked on at school, but when the local mall is attacked by a monstrous supervillain called Giganta, she discovers that tiny Bumblebee might be the only one small enough to save the day.

title: Steven Universe the Movie: Change Song
description: Change (feat. Zach Callison) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: A Line in the Sand
description: While the Ninja fight to save MegaMonster Amusement Park, Jay struggles to defend his family's home from the Vermillion Warriors. But the arrival of the Emerald Time Blade, with its ability to slow time, leads to a desert chase as the heroes try to reach the Blade before the snakes get it!

title: Gut Feelings
description: With help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword, the Warriors help get to the root of who stole all the vegetable Magiswords that belong to the angry bunny, Hoppus.

title: The Girlfriend
description: Jamie has decided she needs a sweetheart and, unlucky for him, she has decided Darwin is the best candidate.

title: The Ball Pit Car
description: The gang is confronted by a strange new force on a Ball Pit Car adventure.

title: Nueva Mascota
description: Después de que Chata les dijera que no pueden tener una mascota, Vic y Val adoptan un lagarto salvaje, sin conocer sus propiedades mágicas, y deciden mantenerlo en secreto para que Chata no se entere.

title: It'll Take a Miracle!
description: Big Barda's life hangs in the balance when Batman is forced by Darkseid to track down the elusive Mr. Miracle and bring back the anti-life equation he stole from Apokolips.

title: A Split End
description: After replicating Cut Man's powers, Mega Man goes on a perfectionist spree, putting him on a collision course with Cut Man himself, whose latest stint as a hairdresser hasn't helped him overcome his own compulsions.

title: Huyendo de casa
description: Descubriremos el misterioso pasado de Shun, su relación con su padre (un magnate de la industria), y su deseo por tener una familia más unida.

title: The Chrome Car
description: The gang meets a familiar face in a mirrored car.
